Interface ConfigurableProcessingExperiment<C,T,R>

  • Type Parameters:
    C - The type of the configuration interface.
    T - The type of the experiment processing target.
    R - The type of the experiment processing result.
    All Superinterfaces:
    ExperimentType<C,T,R>

    public interface ConfigurableProcessingExperiment<C,T,R>
extends ExperimentType<C,T,R>
    An experiment type which will apply a ConfigurableProcessor to the result of a parent experiment part, and output the result.
